<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.9.8">
<l>nāviṉu ṇiṉṟu malaru ñāṉak kalaikaḷuk kellā</l>
<l>māviyu mākkaiyun tāṉē yaḻippō ṭaḷippavaṉ ṟāṉē</l>
<l>pūviya ṉāṟṟaṭan tōḷaṉ porupaṭai yāḻicaṅ kēntuṅ</l>
<l>kāvinaṉ mēṉik kamalak kaṇṇaṉeṉ kaṇṇiṉu ḷāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Of all the arts of knowledge that bloom, standing on [my] tongue,</l>
<l>soul and body is he, the one of provision along with destruction is he,</l>
<l>he with four broad arms of flower nature, the one the good complexion of a blue lily</l>
<l>who holds up conch [and] discus as [his] fighting weapon, the one with lotus eyes is in my eyes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
